		<img class="float-right w-64 h-64" src="https://st2.depositphotos.com/5266903/8596/v/450/depositphotos_85963372-stock-illustration-service-tools-icon.jpg"/>
		<p> <b>Controle de ordens de serviço</b> - Projeto consiste em um sistema para gerenciamento de ordens de serviço.  </p>
	
		<img class="float-right w-64 h-64" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Pokebola-pokeball-png-0.png/800px-Pokebola-pokeball-png-0.png"/>
		<p>Maybe we can live without libraries, people like you and me</p>
  
  
  </div>
  
	  
	  </div>

</section>

<Sobre/>

